    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Requires PHP >= 5.5`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Updated to use PSR-7`}
        <ul parentName="li">
          <li parentName="ul">{`Requires immutable messages, which basically means an event based system
owned by a request instance is no longer possible.`}</li>
          <li parentName="ul">{`Utilizing the `}<a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "https://github.com/guzzle/psr7"
