        </ul>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Clients no longer accept an array of URI template string and variables for
URI variables. You will need to expand URI templates before passing them
into a client constructor or request method.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Client methods `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`get()`}</inlineCode>{`, `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`post()`}</inlineCode>{`, `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`put()`}</inlineCode>{`, `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`patch()`}</inlineCode>{`, `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`options()`}</inlineCode>{`, etc. are
