      <li parentName="ul">{`Replaced `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`Utils.php`}</inlineCode>{` with plain functions in `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`functions.php`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Removed `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`GuzzleHttp\\Collection`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Removed `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`GuzzleHttp\\BatchResults`}</inlineCode>{`. Batched pool results are now returned as
an array.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Removed `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`GuzzleHttp\\Query`}</inlineCode>{`. Query string handling is now handled using an
associative array passed into the `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`query`}</inlineCode>{` request option. The query string
