for the HTTP request functions from function.php, these functions are now
implemented in `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`GuzzleHttp\\Utils`}</inlineCode>{` using camelCase. `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`GuzzleHttp\\json_decode`}</inlineCode>{`
